Duchess drink is a classic dessert drink made from an infusion of the eponymous pear variety with juicy and sweet pulp according to a classic recipe.

Using only the best ingredients, natural pear flavors, the purest artesian water and natural sugar, the highest quality is ensured and a bright taste and unique aroma are imparted.

Baltika No. 7 Export is a light filtered beer, a classic European lager with a mild and rich taste. The product leads the premium beer segment from the Baltika brewery. This drink appeared in 1994, and its release was dedicated to the beginning of the Goodwill Games held in St. Petersburg. Beer belongs to the "export" category, as it is supplied to more than 40 countries of the world. More: https://winestyle.ru
